msgid ""
"Only works with vllm merged `VLLM_PR_23620 <https://github.com/vllm-"
"project/vllm/pull/23620>`_"
msgstr "仅适用于合并了 `VLLM_PR_23620 <https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/pull/23620>`_ 的 vllm"

